Exactly. We did it on purpose. Welcome to this deep dive. Today, we are completely dismantling how you see the built environment.

00:46.380 --> 00:53.020
Yeah, we really are, because, you know, we built an entire global civilization on a structural illusion.

00:53.360 --> 00:54.720
A structural illusion.

