10:14.040 --> 10:23.580
That is exactly what we did. We zeroed out the thermal and hydrological capacities and substituted them with massive external energy expenditure.

10:23.580 --> 10:26.220
The physical laws of the universe didn't change.

10:26.400 --> 10:31.940
